latestIgtvVideos.title: 1 base look  5 outfits! 🖤✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Choose your black fit. 👀 
These are super easy and chic.
.
 Just by adding a third layer/piece and some accessories you can make your all black outfit interesting and edgy.❤️ 
.
Throw on an overcoat, jacket or any sweater, wear your favourite gold accessories, a sling bag and your winter cap. 
Voila! You're good to go. 
.
Also by adding some prints you can change the whole vibe like I did in the last one. ✨ (layering it up) 
.
.
Let me know your fav? Mine is last one. 🤍
.

.
